</p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The information we collect from you may be used in a number of ways, including to improve our services and/or to stay in touch. We use this information to better respond to your individual requests for products, services, and information, to provide information about products, information and services that we think you may be interested in, to refine our website and digital offerings, improve customer service, and to send periodic emails and/or newsletters if you opt-in for this communication.</span></p>
